songs.title: High Speed
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Can anybody fly this thing?
Before my head explodes
Or my head starts to ring

We've been living life inside a bubble
We've been living life inside a bubble

[Chorus]
Confidence in you
Is confidence in me
Is confidence in high speed

[Verse 2]
Can anybody stop this thing?
Before my head explodes
Or my head starts to ring

We've been living life inside a bubble
We've been living life inside a bubble

[Chorus]
Confidence in you
Is confidence in me
Is confidence in high speed

[Outro]
In high speed
High speed

High speed you on
High speed you on
High speed you on
High speed you on
